ConstValues.value:
"query GRIGEntity($criteria: String, $count: Int, $page: Int, $generation: Int) {
  ranking(
    criteria: $criteria
    count: $count
    page: $page
    generation: $generation
  ) {
    __typename
    name
    nickname
    bio
    avatar_url
    pullRequests
    stared
    issues
    generation
    forked
    following
    followers
    contributions
  }
}"
